          <section>
            <title>The Fed Governor's speech</title>
            <subtitle>Consequences in different countries</title>
            <chapter>
              <title>United States</title>
              <paragraph>While she penalizes the dollar on the currency market, recently it wobbled. After two months
                of nightmare, the US stock has reacted well. For all three stocks would be the best monthly performance since October.</paragraph>
              </chapter>
              <graph unit="USD" x="date" y="number">
                <title>The US Stock Market Reaction</title>
                <dataset label= "">
