                      <title>Has the American Dream come to an end?</title>
                      <chapter>
                        <paragraph>Employment growth remains strong but wages grew a mere 2.3% compared to a year ago. It’s especially disappointing because the economy has added millions of jobs in the last two years. When job growth increases, wages tend to follow with it.</paragraph>
